  "source_text": {
    "text_id": "text_001",
    "title": "与同事在咖啡馆短暂休憩、闲聊",
    "source": "教师提供",
    "raw_text": "我看了眼时钟，拒绝了加班，露出微笑，伸手关掉了电脑。我们两人一起下楼，走向星巴克。我看着红衣服的同事，他挥了挥手，我们便坐了下来。同事和我聊起天来：“这天气时晴时阴，眼看又要下雨了……” 我听着，心里有点无奈，又有点不安。 我笑着说：“来杯咖啡和牛角包。” 同事笑着回应：“我来杯绿茶，再加个苹果。”我们坐着，有一搭没一搭地聊着天。 同事端着绿茶说：“看世界杯，巴西对葡萄牙！”我忍不住笑了。 我捧着咖啡说：“看这球赛的精彩瞬间！” 同事又说：“最近在找房子。” 我接话：“刚看新闻，说房价跌了。” 我又补了句：“不过油价倒是涨了！” 同事说：“我看股票涨了。” 同事又吐槽：“油价涨得离谱，车都快开不起了！”他看起来有点生气。 我叹了口气：“我看的股票跌了。” 同事说：“汇率倒是涨了。”我们就这么聊着天。 我们挥手告别，他下楼，我往楼上走。 时钟滴答走着，我上了楼，左转右转，朝着洗手间走去。 我心里想着卫生棉条的事，走进洗手间，看着棉条，拉上了隔间的拉链。 我看着棉条，发了会儿呆。 走出隔间，我有点懵，耳边好像响起了音乐，看着不远处的女生，她回头看了我一眼。 我看着她，想起她整理衣服的样子，心里有点心动。时钟继续走着，我往工位走，想起了垃圾分类的事。我把垃圾丢了，走回工位，坐了下来。",
    "notes": "用于自然语言文本标注示例"
  },
  "units": [
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_001",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看了眼时钟，拒绝了加班，露出微笑，伸手关掉了电脑。",
      "sentence_index": 1,
      "char_start": 0,
      "char_end": 46,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_002",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们两人一起下楼，走向星巴克。",
      "sentence_index": 2,
      "char_start": 47,
      "char_end": 72,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_003",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着红衣服的同事，他挥了挥手，我们便坐了下来。",
      "sentence_index": 3,
      "char_start": 73,
      "char_end": 114,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_004",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事和我聊起天来：“这天气时晴时阴，眼看又要下雨了……”",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "char_start": 115,
      "char_end": 174,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_005",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我听着，心里有点无奈，又有点不安。",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "char_start": 175,
      "char_end": 210,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_006",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我笑着说：“来杯咖啡和牛角包。”",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "char_start": 211,
      "char_end": 246,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_007",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事笑着回应：“我来杯绿茶，再加个苹果。”",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "char_start": 247,
      "char_end": 292,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_008",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们坐着，有一搭没一搭地聊着天。",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "char_start": 293,
      "char_end": 326,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_009",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事端着绿茶说：“看世界杯，巴西对葡萄牙！”",
      "sentence_index": 9,
      "char_start": 327,
      "char_end": 376,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_010",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我忍不住笑了。",
      "sentence_index": 10,
      "char_start": 377,
      "char_end": 392,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_011",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我捧着咖啡说：“看这球赛的精彩瞬间！”",
      "sentence_index": 11,
      "char_start": 393,
      "char_end": 434,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_012",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事又说：“最近在找房子。”",
      "sentence_index": 12,
      "char_start": 435,
      "char_end": 464,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_013",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我接话：“刚看新闻，说房价跌了。”",
      "sentence_index": 13,
      "char_start": 465,
      "char_end": 502,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_014",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我又补了句：“不过油价倒是涨了！”",
      "sentence_index": 14,
      "char_start": 503,
      "char_end": 538,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_015",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事说：“我看股票涨了。”",
      "sentence_index": 15,
      "char_start": 539,
      "char_end": 566,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_016",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事又吐槽：“油价涨得离谱，车都快开不起了！”",
      "sentence_index": 16,
      "char_start": 567,
      "char_end": 622,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_017",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "他看起来有点生气。",
      "sentence_index": 17,
      "char_start": 623,
      "char_end": 644,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_018",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我叹了口气：“我看的股票跌了。”",
      "sentence_index": 18,
      "char_start": 645,
      "char_end": 680,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_019",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "同事说：“汇率倒是涨了。”",
      "sentence_index": 19,
      "char_start": 681,
      "char_end": 708,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_020",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们就这么聊着天。",
      "sentence_index": 20,
      "char_start": 709,
      "char_end": 728,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_021",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我们挥手告别，他下楼，我往楼上走。",
      "sentence_index": 21,
      "char_start": 729,
      "char_end": 766,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_022",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "时钟滴答走着，我上了楼，左转右转，朝着洗手间走去。",
      "sentence_index": 22,
      "char_start": 767,
      "char_end": 822,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_023",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我心里想着卫生棉条的事，走进洗手间，看着棉条，拉上了隔间的拉链。",
      "sentence_index": 23,
      "char_start": 823,
      "char_end": 898,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_024",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着棉条，发了会儿呆。",
      "sentence_index": 24,
      "char_start": 899,
      "char_end": 924,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_025",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "走出隔间，我有点懵，耳边好像响起了音乐，看着不远处的女生，她回头看了我一眼。",
      "sentence_index": 25,
      "char_start": 925,
      "char_end": 1004,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_026",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着她，想起她整理衣服的样子，心里有点心动。",
      "sentence_index": 26,
      "char_start": 1005,
      "char_end": 1054,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_027",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "时钟继续走着，我往工位走，想起了垃圾分类的事。",
      "sentence_index": 27,
      "char_start": 1055,
      "char_end": 1102,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_028",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我把垃圾丢了，走回工位，坐了下来。",
      "sentence_index": 28,
      "char_start": 1103,
      "char_end": 1142,
      "children": []
    }
  ],
